PLAYER STATS HELP
CHARISMA

Charisma/Charm(CHA): The charm stat is an indicator of your people skills and ability to perform certain types of magic. At the moment, charm doesn't get used for very much, but it will eventually come into play with a very wide array of skills.

See also: ~CREFstats, strength, dexterity, constitution, speed, willpower, empathy, charisma
